story.text: Had so much fun in Maine/ Danced my face off. Really a beautiful wedding filled with love. Really respect John and Kelsey. I am hopeful for their future. Very hopeful they do not end up in Maine and consider eastern shore of Michigan.
I do miss the Ocean, but hope that eastern shore can replace that part of me.
Sounds like Kamila will be moving to Montana at the end of the summer - which is so damn exciting. Very hopeful.
